<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 06:18:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国和朝鲜签署合作誓言纪念建交75周年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-mark-75th-anniversary-ties-with-vows-cooperation-2024-10-05/</link><description>据朝中社报道，中国和朝鲜领导人周日在两国建交 75 周年之际交换了加强双边合作的誓言。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 22:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-mark-75th-anniversary-ties-with-vows-cooperation-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官：应允许中国汽车制造商通过在欧盟投资以避免关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-chinese-automakers-should-be-allowed-avert-tariffs-by-investing-eu-2024-10-05/</link><description>即使德国及其汽车制造商拒绝了，欧盟仍将继续对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 22:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-chinese-automakers-should-be-allowed-avert-tariffs-by-investing-eu-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统称中华人民共和国“不可能”成为我们的祖国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/impossible-peoples-republic-china-be-our-motherland-taiwan-president-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周六表示，中华人民共和国“不可能”成为台湾的祖国，因为台湾有更古老的政治根源。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 13:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/impossible-peoples-republic-china-be-our-motherland-taiwan-president-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，欧盟计划对中国电动汽车征收关税，不利于两国关系和绿色雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-plan-press-ahead-with-china-ev-tariffs-bad-ties-green-ambitions-xinhua-2024-10-05/</link><description>新华社周六表示，欧盟委员会决定对中国制造的电动汽车加征关税，这可能会破坏中国与欧盟数十年的合作，并危及气候变化目标。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 09:12:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-plan-press-ahead-with-china-ev-tariffs-bad-ties-green-ambitions-xinhua-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，刺激措施后中国房屋销售量上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-rise-after-stimulus-measures-state-media-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>官方媒体周六表示，自9月下旬以来，一系列房地产刺激措施提振了中国陷入困境的房地产市场，国庆假期期间中国房屋销售量出现增长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 05:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-rise-after-stimulus-measures-state-media-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>外交部称已有200多名中国公民撤离黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-foreign-ministry-says-2024-10-05/</link><description>中国外交部周六表示，已有200多名中国公民安全撤离黎巴嫩。</description><pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 05:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/more-than-200-chinese-citizens-evacuated-lebanon-foreign-ministry-says-2024-10-05/</guid></item><item><title>两名英国男子否认为中国从事间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-british-men-deny-spying-china-2024-10-04/</link><description>周五，两名英国人对为中国从事间谍活动的指控表示无罪，其中包括一名英国高级议员的前研究员。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-british-men-deny-spying-china-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国敦促欧盟推迟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-delay-implementing-tariffs-china-made-evs-state-media-says-2024-10-04/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国周五呼吁欧盟推迟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，避免贸易摩擦升级。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-delay-implementing-tariffs-china-made-evs-state-media-says-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国在南海袭击越南渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-assaulting-vietnamese-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-04/</link><description>菲律宾周五指责中国海事官员在南中国海有争议的海域对越南渔民进行“无理攻击”，为这场紧张的对抗争端增添了色彩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:55:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-assaulting-vietnamese-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟投票支持对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高额关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-votes-favour-hefty-tariffs-china-made-ev-imports-2024-10-04/</link><description>周五，欧盟支持对中国进口电动汽车（EV）征收高达 45% 的关税，以对抗中国政府对目前针对欧洲的汽车制造商的补贴。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:43:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-votes-favour-hefty-tariffs-china-made-ev-imports-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>专注于中国的对冲基金九月回报爆炸性增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-focused-hedge-funds-post-explosive-september-returns-2024-10-04/</link><description>由于中国政府激进的经济刺激计划推动中国股市大幅反弹，一些专注于中国的对冲基金在 9 月份报告了爆炸性回报。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-focused-hedge-funds-post-explosive-september-returns-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟各国政府如何就中国电动汽车关税进行投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-eu-governments-plan-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会周五表示，在欧盟成员国投票中获得了足够的支持，将对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达45%的关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:38:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-eu-governments-plan-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>在欧盟支持关税后，汽车制造商不计划立即调整中国制造的电动汽车的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/saics-mg-france-will-stick-ev-prices-2024-regardless-outcome-eu-vote-2024-10-04/</link><description>汽车制造商表示，欧盟在周五成员国投票后决定继续对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，预计不会立即引发受影响车辆的价格变化。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:11:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/saics-mg-france-will-stick-ev-prices-2024-regardless-outcome-eu-vote-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟在投票结果存在分歧后继续推进对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-face-pivotal-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</link><description>欧盟执行官周五表示，即使欧盟最大经济体德国拒绝了，欧盟仍将继续对中国制造的电动汽车征收高额关税，这暴露了欧盟与北京十年来最大贸易争端的分歧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 01:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-face-pivotal-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-2024-10-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国的刺激措施吸引投资者重返陷入困境的房地产行业的离岸债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stimulus-draws-investors-back-offshore-bonds-troubled-property-sector-2024-10-03/</link><description>一些中国和全球机构投资者正在重新审视中国房地产债券，押注随着政府加快努力促进经济增长并重振陷入债务危机的房地产行业，前景将有所改善。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 23:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stimulus-draws-investors-back-offshore-bonds-troubled-property-sector-2024-10-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>